  "detailed_description": "<strong>Linked with a Pan-Dimensional Monster, You fight to survive and find your way home…!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1547420/extras/9c110c9a60d66a57eef31ada0170b841.poster.avif?t=1620226777\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1547420/extras/9c110c9a60d66a57eef31ada0170b841.webm?t=1620226777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1547420/extras/9c110c9a60d66a57eef31ada0170b841.mp4?t=1620226777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES: </h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Blast your way through Mind Altering Areas of the Hyades Star Cluster as you journey across the Galaxy. <br><br></li><li>Defend your Symbiotically Bonded Monster from Hordes of Soul Devouring Demiurge spawn and various Tentacled Abominations. <br><br></li><li>Solve 'Colour & Geomancy' Puzzles to Complete Mystical Summoning Rites and bring forth minions of the Archons. <br><br></li><li>Fight your way through Six Unique End Level Bosses. <br><br></li><li>Contemplate the vast mysteries of our Universe via an esoteric plot which combines elements of Lovecraftian Cosmicism, Theosophy and Ancient Gnosticism. <br><br></li><li>All while enjoying the soothing sounds of an Original Dream-Piano Soundtrack.  </li></ul><br><strong>...Stars Now Are Right…!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Linked with a Pan-Dimensional Monster, You fight to survive and find your way home…!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1547420/extras/9c110c9a60d66a57eef31ada0170b841.poster.avif?t=1620226777\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1547420/extras/9c110c9a60d66a57eef31ada0170b841.webm?t=1620226777\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1547420/extras/9c110c9a60d66a57eef31ada0170b841.mp4?t=1620226777\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES: </h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Blast your way through Mind Altering Areas of the Hyades Star Cluster as you journey across the Galaxy. <br><br></li><li>Defend your Symbiotically Bonded Monster from Hordes of Soul Devouring Demiurge spawn and various Tentacled Abominations. <br><br></li><li>Solve 'Colour & Geomancy' Puzzles to Complete Mystical Summoning Rites and bring forth minions of the Archons. <br><br></li><li>Fight your way through Six Unique End Level Bosses. <br><br></li><li>Contemplate the vast mysteries of our Universe via an esoteric plot which combines elements of Lovecraftian Cosmicism, Theosophy and Ancient Gnosticism. <br><br></li><li>All while enjoying the soothing sounds of an Original Dream-Piano Soundtrack.  </li></ul><br><strong>...Stars Now Are Right…!</strong>",
